high_descs: Turn right and face the sink.
Grab the knife from the sink.
Turn around and walk right and face the stove.
Place the knife in the skillet.
Grab the skillet off of the stove.
Turn left and walk so that the sink is on the left.
Place the skillet to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the skillet with the knife in it next to the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the right and head towards the sink.
Grab the knife that is in the sink.
Turn around, go straight, and make a right towards the oven.
Place the knife in the pan that is on the oven burner.
Pick up the pan with the knife in it.
Turn around and head back towards the sink.
Place the pan and knife on top of the sink counter, to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Grab and knife and pan and put them on the sink counter.

high_descs: Turn right to face the sink.
Pick the knife up from out of of the sink.
Turn around then go to the right to face the stove.
Place the knife in the pan on th front left burner.
Pick up the pan with the knife in it.
Turn around then to the left to stand next to the counter.
Place the pan with the knife to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the knife inside of the pan on the counter to the right of the sink.
